MATURATION_PLAN.md

# Private AI-assistant onboarding doc — operator voice, conventions, lessons learned
CLAUDE.md

# Private rolling punch list — short-lived; not for the public repo
TODO.md

# Comprehensive AI-assistant briefing — denormalized snapshot of the project
# state for a cold handoff; longer companion to CLAUDE.md
HANDOFF.md

# Visual brainstorming companion scratch (gitignored)
.superpowers/

